   version stable 1.7.1
   require imake libX11 libXrandr xorg-cf-files
  optional libao   ''                  '' for audio output using libao audio library
  optional openssl --with-openssl=/usr '' use openssl instead of static own binaries
  category utility/terminal-emulator
 attribute x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL rdesktop/rdesktop/$VERSION/rdesktop-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info good 20120702
      info last 20120109
      info home http://www.rdesktop.org
      desc 'connect to Windows terminal servers
rdesktop is an open source client for Windows NT Terminal Server and
Windows 2000 Terminal Services, capable of natively speaking Remote
Desktop Protocol (RDP) in order to present the user NT desktop.'

build(){
./configure   \
--prefix=/usr \
$OPTS &&
make  &&
make install DESTDIR=$DESTDIR
}
